author: Associated Press
title: Utah State pulls upset on No. 21 Boise State
text: Marwin Evans returned an interception 90 yards for a touchdown as time expired before halftime, and host Utah State turned Boise State’s seven first-half turnovers into 35 points in the Aggies’ 52-26 victory over the No. 21 Broncos on Friday night.
